## TL;DR

This repo IS an Obsidian vault. It holds structured, LLM-maintained knowledge about {{DOMAIN_DESCRIPTION}} for the {{PROJECT_NAME}} project. Raw capture arrives via the {{AGENT_NAME}} agent; Claude Code classifies and writes structured pages under `wiki/` on a schedule driven by {{OPS_REPO}}.

**One sentence:** *Capture in → raw file → scheduled classification → structured Obsidian wiki out.*

