## Backup and disaster recovery

This vault is one of the repos managed by {{OPS_REPO}}. Backup cadence, lockfile discipline, bulk-delete tripwires, and restore runbook all live there. Never run `git push --force`, `git reset --hard`, or `git commit --amend` against this repo from inside an LLM session — if something looks broken, stop and read {{OPS_REPO}}'s RESTORE runbook.

