## Operating commands

```
/{{VAULT_NAME}}-ingest       # Pass 1 + Pass 2 — classify and write wiki updates
/{{VAULT_NAME}}-compile      # rebuild wiki/index.md from current wiki/ state
/{{VAULT_NAME}}-query "..."  # ad-hoc question; answer saved to wiki/outputs/
/{{VAULT_NAME}}-lint         # health check; report saved to wiki/outputs/
```

Ingest runs automatically via {{OPS_REPO}}'s launchd/cron jobs; the others are manual.

